reviewText: the stuff the cute little kids said on the dvd was to funny. it had me laughing alot!
This was fun nostalgia-wise, but it didn't seem that they chose the best episodes and they didn't edit it much.  I also got Volumes 1 and 2 and they were about the same.

This is number 3 of three volumes of 24 x 5-minute segments from 24 different HOUSE PARTY TV-episodes, circa: 1967-1969. Art Linkletter (1912-2010)-- and I thought ==> I <== was "older than dirt! Hosted a few radio & TV shows[*] up till about the time I was shipped off to Vietnam [*]= denotes, see also : People Are Funny (16 Episodes on 3 Discs) People Are Funny Let Me In, I Hear Laughter - A Salute to the Friars Club People Are Funny - Art Linkletter - Classic Movie Here's Lucy: Season Three -- Art Linkletter GUEST-stars in --- what else? --- THE ART LINKLETTER SHOW.
